{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"WebRTC","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Glossary/WebRTC","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><span class=\"seoSummary\"><strong>WebRTC</strong> (<em>Web Real-Time Communication</em>)はビデオチャット、音声通話、P2P ファイル共有を行うウェブアプリで使われる API です。</span></p>\n\n<p>WebRTC は主に以下の要素で構成されています:</p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"getusermedia\"><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaDevices/getUserMedia\" title=\"getUserMedia()\"><code>getUserMedia()</code></a></dt>\n <dd>端末のカメラとマイクのアクセスを許可し、シグナルと RTC接続を繋ぎます。</dd>\n <dt id=\"rtcpeerconnection\"><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/RTCPeerConnection\"><code>RTCPeerConnection</code></a></dt>\n <dd>ビデオチャットまたは音声通話を構成するインターフェイスです。</dd>\n <dt id=\"sect1\">&nbsp;<a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/RTCDataChannel\"><code>RTCDataChannel</code></a></dt>\n <dd>ブラウザー間の<a href=\"/ja/docs/Glossary/P2P\">P2P</a> のデータ経路を構成するメソッド。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"詳細情報","title":"詳細情報","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li>Wikipedia 上の記事「<a title=\"WebRTC\" href=\"https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/WebRTC\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">WebRTC</a>」</li>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/WebRTC_API\">MDN上の WebRTC の解説</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"http://caniuse.com/#feat=rtcpeerconnection\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">WebRTC のブラウザーサポート状況</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"詳細情報","id":"詳細情報"}],"summary":"WebRTC (Web Real-Time Communication)はビデオチャット、音声通話、P2P ファイル共有を行うウェブアプリで使われる API です。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"WebRTC","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"WebRTC","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"WebRTC","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"WebRTC","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"WebRTC","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"WebRTC","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/glossary/webrtc","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/glossary/webrtc/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Glossary","title":"MDN Web Docs 用語集: ウェブ関連用語の定義"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Glossary/WebRTC","title":"WebRTC"}],"pageTitle":"WebRTC - MDN Web Docs 用語集: ウェブ関連用語の定義 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}